name: Key Signing Party Tools
tagline: Tools for people who attend key signing parties
body:
### Key Signing Party Tools

This is a project for creating a set of tools making key signing parties more convenient. It aims to automate the boring parts of the process while keeping things secure.

The project is currently in an alpha stage.
